title: Woodhead Publishing Series in Composites Science and Engineering
description:
[Updated at 2016.09.16]

The Composites Science and Engineering Series is a collection of reference books that encourage learning and innovation on a range of different topics and provide understanding to scientists and engineers working outside their own area of expertise. The competitive advantage of the series is that it provides comprehensive coverage of major trends in latest research striving to promote and progress the exchange of specialist knowledge
